title: Weapon of Desire - L. M. Brook.epub
description:
Are you drunk and senseless on a cocktail of love following a delusional path? 
Is the hot passion flowing through your veins compromising your better judgement? Darcey Brooks trades trust and honesty with lies and deceit when she becomes drawn into a dark world of deadly secrets. Intrigued and captivated by Anthony Hunt the new Head of Strategy and Development at Dorton Airfield; life swiftly spins dangerously out of control. 
Who can she trust? How can she survive? Lie?... Steal?... Take another man's life? Can you trust the person with whom you share your bed?

Genre: Romance
